1. *Bobi* se igrao sa svojim prijateljima. (He was playing with his friends.)
2. *Bobi* je bio dobar učenik. (He was a good student.)
3. *Bobija* je često volela da pravi svojim roditeljima. (She often liked to make it for her parents.)
4. *Bobiju* je majka često hranila voćem. (His mother often fed him fruit.)
5. *Bobija* su često zvali da se igraju sa drugom decom. (He was often called to play with other children.)